rules.name: Share what you're working on
rules.description: Don't be scared to share unfinished work

rules.name: Screenshots, screencasts, drafts, etc
rules.description: Visual tweets tend to grab people's attention

rules.name: No self-promotion
rules.description: Don't ask for upvotes or advertise your products/services.

rules.name: Stay on-topic
rules.description: Only post about building in public. No politics or other off-topic posts. There are other communities for that.

rules.name: No engagement farming
rules.description: If your goal is to get replies, likes, etc, dont post it here. Dont ask super generic questions like whats everyone working on?

rules.name: Use a personal account
rules.description: No company accounts. No logos. Use your own name. No promotion or URLs in your name.
